Copied!
Update config.yaml
On your main server, update the store section in config.yaml to use PostgreSQL:

server:
  # ... existing settings ...

  store:
    engine: "postgres"
    dsn: "host=postgres-server user=postgres password=password dbname=postgres port=5432"

